      • getLocation

        public Location getLocation(World world,
                            int chunkX,
                            int chunkZ)
        Retrieve the location of this block change.

        The world and absolute chunk position must be provided.

        参数:
        world - - the world the block belongs to.
        chunkX - - the x position of the origin chunk
        chunkZ - - the y position of the origin chunk
        返回:
        The location.
